project_name: SITC of 33kV transmission line with 433V LT distribution panels and supply of cables
technical_specifications:
Supply, Installation, Testing, Commissioning 33kV Transmission line
Supply, Installation, Testing, Commissioning LT Distribution Panels including Switchgear, Cu Busbar, MCB/MCCB, RYB indication, On/off Indication, Earthing etc.
Supply of Cables, PVC Casing Capping & Accessories
Brass Glands for PVC cables of Voltage Grade up to and including 3.3 kV as per IS:12943
